                "content": "<p>Try It Out!</p><p>Enable automatic token swaps on a predefined schedule:</p><p></p><p>Use cases are many: Automate your ETH to USDC conversions daily (or on any custom schedule) without manual trades:</p><p></p><p>How it works:</p><p></p><p>A Schedule Trigger starts the workflow at a set time (default: 9 AM daily).</p><p></p><p>The Set Swap Details node defines swap parameters:</p><p></p><p>FromToken = ETH</p><p></p><p>ToToken = USDC</p><p></p><p>Amount = 0.01 (default, adjustable)</p><p></p><p>Slippage = 0.5%</p><p></p><p>The AFKCrypto Swap API executes the trade from ETH â†’ USDC.</p><p></p><p>How to use:</p><p></p><p>Update the walletAddress in the Set Swap Details node with your AFK wallet.</p><p></p><p>Adjust fromToken and toToken addresses if you want to swap other tokens.</p><p></p><p>Update the amount and slippage values as needed.</p><p></p><p>Set your own schedule in the Schedule Trigger node.</p><p></p><p>Link your AFK Crypto API key in the HTTP Request node credentials.</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p></p><p>AFK Crypto account and API key (www.afkcrypto.com</p><p>)</p><p></p><p>Make instance with access to HTTP Request nodes</p><p></p><p>A wallet funded with ETH (to perform swaps)</p><p></p><p>ðŸ’± Swap Smarter, Not Harder!</p>",
